Hi @david-garcia-garcia and thanks for your contribution!

While the change makes sense functionally, it could be a good idea to document the security implications of enabling syscall access in plugins, since syscall provides low-level system access.

@juliens @rtribotte @kevinpollet, any idea of the location of such documentation to update?

Thanks 👍

@idurgakalyan I made some changes, and everything sounds ok on my end.
We are now waiting for another review before merging.
